@startuml Recognize and Update Meal - Sequence Diagram

!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60

title Valdyti patiekalą: Atpažinti maistą iš nuotraukos ir atnaujinti patiekalą

actor "Šeimos\nnarys" as User
participant "MealPlanningPage\n<<screen>>" as Page
participant "MealPlanningController\n<<control>>" as Controller
participant "CameraGalleryBoundary\n<<boundary>>" as Camera
participant "ImageProcessingService" as ImageService
participant "GeminiServiceBoundary\n<<boundary>>" as Gemini
participant "ProductEntity\n<<entity>>" as Product
participant "DishEntity\n<<entity>>" as Dish
participant "MealPlanningService" as MealService
participant "SupabaseClient\n(Core.Network)" as Supabase
database "Supabase DB\n(meal_plans)" as Database

== SCENARIJUS: Vartotojas redaguoja patiekalą ir atpažįsta maistą ==

User -> Page: Atidaro MealPlanningPage\n(šiandienos valgiai)
activate Page

Page -> Controller: LoadMealPlanEvent(date: today)
activate Controller

note right of Controller: **BE REPOSITORY:**\nController tiesiogiai naudoja\nSupabaseClient

Controller -> Supabase: from('meal_plans')\n  .select()\n  .eq('user_id', userId)\n  .eq('date', date)
activate Supabase
Supabase -> Database: SELECT * FROM meal_plans\nWHERE user_id = ? AND date = ?
activate Database
Database --> Supabase: JSON data
deactivate Database
Supabase --> Controller: List<Map<String, dynamic>>
deactivate Supabase

Controller -> Controller: mapToMealPlanEntity(data)

Controller --> Page: MealPlanLoadedState(meals: [...])
deactivate Controller

Page -> User: Rodo šiandienos valgius:\n- Pusryčiai\n- Pietūs\n- Vakarienė
deactivate Page

note right of User: Vartotojas mato planuotą valgį\n(pvz., "Pietūs: Blynai")

User -> Page: Paspaudžia "Redaguoti" ant valgio
activate Page

Page -> Controller: EditMealEvent(mealId, mealType)
activate Controller

Controller -> Supabase: from('meals')\n  .select()\n  .eq('id', mealId)\n  .single()
activate Supabase
Supabase -> Database: SELECT * FROM meals WHERE id = ?
activate Database
Database --> Supabase: JSON data
deactivate Database
Supabase --> Controller: Map<String, dynamic>
deactivate Supabase

Controller -> Controller: mapToMealEntity(data)

Controller --> Page: MealEditState(meal: currentMeal)
deactivate Controller

Page -> User: Rodo redagavimo formą:\n- Pavadinimas: "Blynai"\n- Ingredientai\n- [Redaguoti ranka]\n- [Atpažinti maistą] ←
deactivate Page

User -> Page: Paspaudžia "Atpažinti maistą"
activate Page

== Nuotraukos pasirinkimas ==

Page -> Camera: requestImage()\n(source: gallery or camera)
activate Camera

Camera -> User: Rodo pasirinkimą:\n📷 Kamera arba 🖼️ Galerija
User -> Camera: Pasirenka nuotrauką

alt Nuotraukos pasirinkimas sėkmingas
    Camera --> Page: File (image file)
    deactivate Camera
    
    Page -> Controller: RecognizeFoodEvent(image: File)
    activate Controller
    
    Page --> User: Rodo "Apdorojama..." indikatorių
    deactivate Page
    
    == Vaizdo apdorojimas ==
    
    Controller -> ImageService: processImage(image)
    activate ImageService
    
    ImageService -> ImageService: Patikrinti formatą\n(JPEG, PNG)
    
    alt Nuotraukos dydis per didelis (>20MB)
        ImageService -> ImageService: Resize ir compress\n(neišmetant spalvų)
    endif
    
    ImageService -> ImageService: Konvertuoti į base64\n(formatą API)
    
    ImageService --> Controller: ProcessedImage(base64, metadata)
    deactivate ImageService
    
    == Maisto atpažinimas per Gemini API ==
    
    Controller -> Gemini: recognizeFood(image: base64)
    activate Gemini
    
    note right of Gemini: **Gemini API Request:**\n- Image base64\n- Prompt: "Identify food in image"\n- Return: product name, category,\n  nutrition info (per 100g/ml)
    
    Gemini -> Gemini: **API Call**\nPOST https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1/models/gemini-pro-vision
    
    Gemini --> Controller: FoodRecognitionResult(\n  name: "Blynai su kiauliena",\n  category: "Breakfast",\n  products: [\n    {name: "Kiauliena", weight: "50g"},\n    {name: "Blynai", weight: "200g"}\n  ],\n  nutrition: {calories: 450, ...},\n  confidence: 0.85\n)
    deactivate Gemini
    
    == Produktų identifikavimas ==
    
    Controller -> Product: findProductByName("Kiauliena")
    activate Product
    
Controller -> Supabase: from('products')\n  .select()\n  .ilike('name', '%Kiauliena%')\n  .limit(1)
activate Supabase
Supabase -> Database: SELECT * FROM products\nWHERE name ILIKE '%Kiauliena%'
activate Database
Database --> Supabase: JSON data
deactivate Database
Supabase --> Controller: List<Map<String, dynamic>>
deactivate Supabase

Controller -> Controller: mapToProductEntity(data.firstOrNull)
    
    Product --> Controller: ProductEntity (arba null)
    deactivate Product
    
    note right of Controller: Jei produktas nerastas →\nsukurti naują ProductEntity\nsu Gemini duomenimis
    
    == Dish (patiekalo) sukūrimas/atnaujinimas ==
    
    Controller -> Dish: createFromRecognition(\n  recognitionResult,\n  existingMealId\n)
    activate Dish
    
    Dish -> Dish: **Sukurti/Atnaujinti DishEntity:**\n- name: "Blynai su kiauliena"\n- products: [ProductEntity...]\n- nutrition: {...}\n- mealType: existingMeal.mealType\n- date: today
    
    Dish --> Controller: DishEntity (atnaujintas)
    deactivate Dish
    
    == Meal Plan atnaujinimas duomenų bazėje ==
    
Controller -> Controller: convertDishToJson(newDish)

Controller -> Supabase: from('meal_plans')\n  .update({'meals': updatedMealsJson})\n  .eq('id', mealPlanId)
activate Supabase

Supabase -> Database: UPDATE meal_plans\nSET meals = jsonb_set(meals, '{meal_id}', ?)\nWHERE id = ?
activate Database
Database --> Supabase: Success
deactivate Database

Supabase --> Controller: Updated JSON
deactivate Supabase

Controller -> Controller: mapToMealPlanEntity(updatedData)
    
    Controller --> Page: MealUpdatedState(\n  meal: updatedDish,\n  message: "Patiekalas atnaujintas!"\n)
    deactivate Controller
    
    Page -> User: Rodo sėkmės pranešimą:\n✅ "Patiekalas atnaujintas!\nIš nuotraukos atpažinta:\n• Blynai su kiauliena\n• 450 kcal"
    deactivate Page
    
    User -> Page: Mato atnaujintą patiekalą
    activate Page
    Page --> User: Rodo naują valgį su atpažintais produktais
    deactivate Page

else Nuotraukos pasirinkimas neįvyko (atšaukta)
    Camera --> Page: null (cancelled)
    deactivate Camera
    
    Page --> User: Atšaukta (nei vieno veiksmo)
    deactivate Page
endif

== ALTERNATYVUS SCENARIJUS: Klaida atpažinant ==

alt Gemini API klaida arba nėra produkto nuotraukoje
    Gemini --> Controller: FoodRecognitionError(\n  message: "Nepavyko atpažinti maisto"\n)
    
    Controller --> Page: MealRecognitionErrorState(\n  error: "Nepavyko atpažinti maisto.\nBandykite dar kartą arba įveskite ranka."\n)
    
    Page -> User: Rodo klaidos pranešimą:\n❌ "Nepavyko atpažinti maisto"\n+ [Bandyti dar kartą]\n+ [Įvesti ranka]
    deactivate Page
endif

note over User, Database
  **SVARBU:**
  - Vartotojas redaguoja PATIEKALĄ (meal), kurį šiandien valgė
  - Vietoj rankinio redagavimo, naudoja maisto atpažinimą
  - Sistema atpažįsta produktus iš nuotraukos ir atnaujina meal planą
  - Meal plan atnaujinamas duomenų bazėje (Supabase)
end note

@enduml

